import { Box, Button, Heading, SimpleGrid, Image, Center, Flex } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import NavBar from "../components/Navigasi";
import fish from "../assets/fish.png";
import arrow from "../assets/arrow.png";

const LandingPage = () => {
    return(
        <>
        <NavBar/>
        <Box height="100vh" position="relative" bgSize="cover" bgImage="linear-gradient(to bottom, #FFFFFF , transparent)">
            <SimpleGrid columns={2} spacing={10}>
                <Box paddingLeft='60px' >
                    <Heading fontSize='8xl' paddingTop='52' as='h1' textColor="#4D4D4D"> Solo Mina Fish </Heading>
                    <Heading paddingTop='6' size='2xl' as='h3' textColor='#4CAF4F'> Since 20 Years</Heading>
                    <Heading paddingTop='8' as='h3'>Fish Consumption Supplier</Heading>
                    <Box paddingTop='10'>
                        <Button size='lg' bgColor='#4CAF4F' textColor='white'>Contact</Button>
                    </Box>
                </Box>
                <Box paddingTop='44' paddingLeft='32'>
                    <Image src={fish} alt="fish assets" width='450px' height='450px'></Image>
                </Box>
            </SimpleGrid>
            <Flex justifyContent='flex-end' marginTop='30px'>
                <Image src={arrow} boxSize="50px"></Image>
            </Flex>
        </Box>

        <Box height='100vh'position="relative" bgColor="#FFFFFF" bgSize="cover">
            <Center textColor="#4D4D4D" fontWeight='semibold' fontSize='2xl'>
                Our Customers
            </Center>
            <Center textColor="#4D4D4D" fontWeight='normal' fontSize='xl'>
                We have been supplied with some 100+ customers
            </Center>
        </Box>
        </>
    )
};

export default LandingPage;
